snippet.title: Cosmonaut - Trailer
snippet.description:
Cosmonaut is a game available on Android, Windows and Mac
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.cosmonaut.android
Desktop: https://apprenticesoft.itch.io/cosmonaut

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
After crossing the asteroid barrier, your spaceship is damaged.
No more oxygen!
No more artificial gravity!
In order to survive you must reach the survival capsule using your space suit and your jetpack.

Cosmonaut counts 24 levels.
For each level, the amount of oxygen and the amount of fuel are limited.
Use your jetpack wisely!


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
For more informations on my projects follow me :
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/Apprentice-Soft-157533514581396/timeline/
Twitter : https://twitter.com/ApprenticeSoft

To play my games, see the Google Play Store : https://play.google.com/store/apps/developer?id=Apprentice+Soft

Music by Kevin MacLeod: http://incompetech.com/wordpress/
